<P>
 Three Popular Antibiotics Recalled: Eli Lilly & Co. recalled 4 million bottles 
of Ceclor, Lorabid and Keflex after small plastic caps were found in four 
bottles of medicine.Anyone taking the drugs should immediately stop and call 
their doctor, the Food and Drug Administration said. The Indianapolis-based 
