<DOCNO> LA040294-0064 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 028466 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 2, 1994, Saturday, Home Edition 
</P>
