<HEADLINE>
<P>
REP. YOUNG TO RUN AGAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Rep. Don Young (R-Alaska) has announced his bid for reelection to the state's 
lone U.S. House seat. Young, from the interior Alaska village of Ft. Yukon, 
will be seeking his 12th term in Congress. 
</P>
