<HEADLINE>
<P>
HERE'S A KING WHO DOESN'T POLISH HIS OWN CROWN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 What a joy and privilege to share the moment with "The Great One" after his 
record-breaking 802nd goal. 
</P>
<P>
 To those of us subjected to awards ceremonies weekly, who read and hear 
professionals tout their greatness daily, it is indeed refreshing to see one 
who is so willing to share. Once again we are reminded that the truly Great 
Ones don't need to remind everyone that "now I am the greatest," a la Rickey 
Henderson. Indeed, Gretzky was quite willing to share and thank all. He is, 
indeed, without equal, and a first class person. 
</P>
<P>
 JAQUIE ROBINSON 
</P>
<P>
 Orange 
