IT WAS OK FOR MILLER TO READ AYRES' MAIL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Why is Cheryl Miller taking heat over a stupid mistake made by Debbie Ayres? 
If Ayres was dumb enough not to verify what hotel Pat Summit was staying at and 
to leave an envelope of valuable information unsealed, why should Miller be 
blamed for reading it? Who wouldn't do the same? 
</P>
<P>
 Cheryl Miller should be getting accolades, not the snide remarks made by some 
of her fellow coaches and the media. Miller is obviously a winner at whatever 
she does and there are a lot of petty people out there who are consumed by 
jealousy over this fact. 
