<DOCID> 028618 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
April 2, 1994, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 2; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
