<TEXT>
<P>
 Caltrans officials announced that concrete median barriers will be installed 
in Santa Clarita beginning this summer. 
</P>
<P>
 The California Transportation Commission on Thursday allocated $1.4 million to 
install a concrete median barrier along a 3 1/2-mile stretch of the Antelope 
Valley Freeway in Santa Clarita.  
