<P>
 Conductor's father -- Felix Slatkin was a member of the St. Louis Symphony 
from 1933-37, but did not hold the position of assistant concertmaster, as was 
stated in a Tuesday's Calendar story about the appointment of his son, Leonard 
Slatkin, as music director of the National Symphony. 
